周一成”，意为香港电影的票房保证。多次获得香港金像奖的最佳动作设计奖，并两度获得台湾电影金马奖最佳男主角奖。成龙以功夫片著称，曾多次打破香港电影票房纪录，其主演的电影全球总票房已经超过200亿元，为华人演员之首。成龙的成名作是《醉拳》；1994年由他主演的《红番区》在美国公映后反响强烈，使其成功打入好莱坞；《尖峰时刻》系列电影亦获得极高的票房，并奠定其国际电影巨星的地位。\r\n广告\r\n　　奇强洗衣粉\r\n成龙 代言佳能EOS(7张) \r\n　　格力空调（倡议支持国产） \r\n　　新日电动车 \r\n　　小霸王学习机 \r\n　　爱多vcd（里面有很经典的一个镜头，取自和唐季礼合作的《简单任务》） \r\n　　劲隆摩托 \r\n　　霸王洗发水　 \r\n　　思念水饺 \r\n　　原叶绿茶 \r\n　　佳能EOS \r\n　　北方汽修 \r\n　　卡巴斯基 \r\n　　汾煌可乐", "short_content": "", "type": 3, "state": 0, "ctime": 1436866637, "count": {"view": 0, "use": 0, "atten": 0}, "is_atten": 0, "likes": 0, "hates": 0, "attribute": 0, "liked": 0, "hated": 0, "extra_attr": 0}, "day_count": 1}, "286537": {"data": {"tag_id": 286537, "tag_name": "杰米", "cover": "", "head_cover": "", "content": "", "short_content": "", "type": 3, "state": 0, "ctime": 1436866637, "count": {"view": 0, "use": 0, "atten": 0}, "is_atten": 0, "likes": 0, "hates": 0, "attribute": 0, "liked": 0, "hated": 0, "extra_attr": 0}, "day_count": 1}, "366": {"data": {"tag_id": 366, "tag_name": "拳皇", "cover": "http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/tag/99f10b9a5e7786b6bf36be5d9124b1c5636d289b.jpg", "head_cover": "", "content": "", "short_content": "", "type": 3, "state": 0, "ctime": 1436866637, "count": {"view": 0, "use": 0, "atten": 0}, "is_atten": 0, "likes": 0, "hates": 0, "attribute": 0, "liked": 0, "hated": 0, "extra_attr": 0}, "day_count": 1}, "1833": {"data": {"tag_id": 1833, "tag_name": "搞笑", "cover": "http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/4afb90b88597f226d22fdaed28a5c4769b372fdc.png", "head_cover": "", "content": "一起进来每日补充沙雕能量", "short_content": "今天你笑出声了吗？", "type": 3, "state": 0, "ctime": 1436866637, "count": {"view": 0, "use": 0, "atten": 0}, "is_atten": 0, "likes": 0, "hates": 0, "attribute": 0, "liked": 0, "hated": 0, "extra_attr": 0}, "day_count": 3}, "47988": {"data": {"tag_id": 47988, "tag_name": "我的世界", "cover": "http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/2baa938d85ba419e0c6a6da9e14cd4cd27fb977e.jpg", "head_cover": "http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/4ee35ed657641b7db26acf3699d9813266f4b353.png", "co